Yixi.

00:02:00.599 --> 00:02:01.120
Yixi.

00:02:01.700 --> 00:02:02.299
Wake up.

00:02:02.760 --> 00:02:03.439
Yixi.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.120
Yixi!

00:02:07.959 --> 00:02:08.400
Yixi?

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:24.400
Still dozing off?

00:02:24.780 --> 00:02:26.099
Do you know who's locked inside?

00:02:26.539 --> 00:02:28.180
It's the vessel sealing the Night Deity.

00:02:29.020 --> 00:02:30.539
She could turn into him at any moment.

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:31.680
Stay alert.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:33.039
Such a terrifying figure.

00:02:33.159 --> 00:02:34.280
Yet assigned to our custody.

00:02:34.460 --> 00:02:35.180
What rotten luck.

00:02:41.439 --> 00:02:42.719
Fate plays cruel tricks.

00:02:43.539 --> 00:02:44.379
For years,

00:02:44.979 --> 00:02:48.219
Nine Heavens has failed
to select a suitable Sword Master.

00:02:49.180 --> 00:02:51.139
Yet the Night Deity stirs restlessly,

00:02:51.620 --> 00:02:53.139
attempting to break the seal.

00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:54.879
The urgent matter now

00:02:55.500 --> 00:02:57.180
is to choose
from immortal sect disciples

00:02:57.520 --> 00:03:00.439
a Sword Master who meets
the Divine Sword's approval

00:03:01.460 --> 00:03:02.659
to safeguard the seal

00:03:03.259 --> 00:03:04.699
and protect all living beings.

00:03:05.259 --> 00:03:06.020
Understood.

