♪Looking at the sky's edge♪

00:04:22.496 --> 00:04:25.731
♪Listening to endless echoes♪

00:04:26.439 --> 00:04:27.639
(I was too weak.)

00:04:28.199 --> 00:04:29.279
(I failed to protect you.)

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:33.200
(The Immortal Lord said they'll select
a Sword Master to guard the seal.)

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:34.600
(Yixi,)

00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:37.360
(I'll become the Sword Master for you.)

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:39.720
(I swear to protect you.)

00:04:40.992 --> 00:04:42.880
♪How to ask when you'll return?♪

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:44.738
♪How vast this world remains♪

00:04:44.738 --> 00:04:48.192
♪If only rain carried news of you♪

00:04:51.620 --> 00:04:53.300
Such beautiful snowfall.

00:04:55.620 --> 00:04:57.339
If only you were here with me.

00:05:53.980 --> 00:05:56.899
All immortals, welcome
Nine Heavens' new Sword Master,

00:05:57.620 --> 00:05:58.899
Wan Guchen!

00:06:11.060 --> 00:06:12.180
I said I wouldn't eat.

00:06:14.139 --> 00:06:14.740
Take it away.

00:06:21.339 --> 00:06:21.939
Chen?

00:06:23.500 --> 00:06:24.139
Chen?

00:06:25.819 --> 00:06:26.579
Is it really you?

00:06:26.980 --> 00:06:27.819
I sneaked in.

00:06:30.339 --> 00:06:30.860
Yixi,

00:06:31.819 --> 00:06:33.060
I have good news.

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:37.240
I'm now Nine Heavens' Sword Master.

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:40.879
You did it.

00:06:41.860 --> 00:06:43.699
From now on, I'll guard your seal.

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:45.839
Then I can convince them to release you.

00:06:53.399 --> 00:06:55.000
I have a gift for you.

00:06:57.300 --> 00:06:58.379
My mother

00:06:59.779 --> 00:07:01.459
left a jade pendant for my beloved.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:03.959
But it's in Wanfeng Kingdom.

00:07:04.959 --> 00:07:06.120
Wait while I retrieve it.

00:07:08.339 --> 00:07:08.699
Okay.

00:07:10.100 --> 00:07:10.779
I'll wait.

00:07:11.699 --> 00:07:12.579
I'll return soon.

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:28.600
Wan Guchen!

00:07:29.319 --> 00:07:30.959
How dare you enter the hall armed?

00:07:31.319 --> 00:07:32.600
You're truly treasonous!

00:07:40.339 --> 00:07:42.139
As the crown prince, my father

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:44.079
was killed by the Night Clan.

00:07:45.740 --> 00:07:47.420
You uncles and elders

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:49.120
feared my inheritance of the throne.

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:51.920
So you fabricated rumors
about my ill omens.

00:07:53.959 --> 00:07:56.839
For years, my grandfather has refused
to reinstall the crown prince.

00:08:00.379 --> 00:08:02.019
So you've always feared me

00:08:03.879 --> 00:08:04.839
and framed me.

00:08:05.959 --> 00:08:07.680
Now I'm the immortal sects'
Sword Master.

00:08:08.459 --> 00:08:10.699
I came only
to retrieve my parents' heirloom

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:13.120
for my beloved.

00:08:14.939 --> 00:08:16.139
If anyone obstructs me again,

00:08:17.459 --> 00:08:19.579
I won't hold back.

00:08:20.860 --> 00:08:21.740
Understood.

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:23.319
Understood.

00:08:39.179 --> 00:08:39.820
War God,

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:41.399
the Immortal Lord awaits you

00:08:41.580 --> 00:08:42.460
for important matters.

00:08:44.139 --> 00:08:44.700
I see.

00:08:50.399 --> 00:08:51.399
Wan Guchen,

00:08:51.799 --> 00:08:52.960
you're finally back.

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:56.200
Immortal Lord,

00:08:56.679 --> 00:08:58.639
Wan Guchen abused
his new Sword Master position

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:00.519
to descend to Wanfeng Kingdom

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.200
and cause chaos with immortal arts.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:04.480
It violates the divine laws.

00:09:11.399 --> 00:09:12.759
Is this true?

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:13.919
No.

00:09:14.580 --> 00:09:17.299
I merely went to the Mortal Realm
to retrieve my parents' keepsake

00:09:17.759 --> 00:09:19.360
to gift it to my beloved.

00:09:19.779 --> 00:09:20.059
You...

00:09:21.220 --> 00:09:23.500
Are you going to see Bai Yixi?

00:09:23.899 --> 00:09:24.379
Exactly.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:28.000
Then I can't allow your meeting.

00:09:29.659 --> 00:09:30.220
Why?

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:34.559
Because Bai Yixi is the Night Deity.

00:09:35.059 --> 00:09:37.220
She's the malevolence
the Three Realms must eradicate.

00:09:37.919 --> 00:09:39.480
No one can visit her.

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.240
This is an order.

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:41.399
Those who defy it

00:09:41.750 --> 00:09:43.600
will be deemed traitors
to the immortal sects.

00:09:45.059 --> 00:09:45.740
What do you mean?

00:09:46.795 --> 00:09:48.035
You said being the Sword Master

00:09:48.430 --> 00:09:50.050
was to safeguard the Night Deity's seal.

00:09:50.940 --> 00:09:52.019
Why can't I see her?

00:09:52.620 --> 00:09:54.740
Was I not explicit enough?

00:09:55.460 --> 00:09:58.100
The Sword Master's duty
isn't merely safeguarding the seal.

00:09:58.419 --> 00:10:02.019
Your true mission is to kill Bai Yixi,
who contains the Night Deity.

00:10:02.220 --> 00:10:05.139
Only this will completely eliminate
the Night Deity.

00:10:11.100 --> 00:10:11.980
What do you mean?

00:10:12.679 --> 00:10:13.840
Have you been deceiving us?

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:16.960
Originally, as the Sword Master,
I should have

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:18.559
personally executed her back then.

00:10:19.460 --> 00:10:21.059
But my fierce battle
with the Night Deity

00:10:21.059 --> 00:10:22.220
left me gravely injured.

00:10:22.259 --> 00:10:24.899
And my diminished cultivation
made the Divine Sword reject me.

00:10:25.379 --> 00:10:29.220
So I needed a new Sword Master
to fulfill heaven's decree.

00:10:30.139 --> 00:10:32.620
Now the seal on her weakens daily.

00:10:33.360 --> 00:10:34.720
I fear the day

00:10:35.220 --> 00:10:37.899
the Night Deity
breaks free from the sealing.

00:10:38.559 --> 00:10:39.879
Then why did you tell me

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:41.300
being the Sword Master

00:10:41.545 --> 00:10:43.065
meant guarding the Night Deity's seal?

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:46.960
Because she's
the Divine Maiden's daughter.

00:10:51.500 --> 00:10:53.740
I couldn't bear revealing
to the immortal sects

00:10:54.860 --> 00:10:56.419
that the target of our execution

00:10:57.100 --> 00:10:58.899
is the Divine Maiden's child.

00:10:59.259 --> 00:11:00.379
But for her,

00:11:01.500 --> 00:11:02.779
isn't it unbearable injustice?

00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:06.179
Shall we let the Night Deity break free
and cast the world into chaos,

00:11:06.179 --> 00:11:07.620
making us eternal sinners,

00:11:07.919 --> 00:11:09.039
or eradicate the Night Deity

00:11:09.159 --> 00:11:10.480
for everyone's sake?

00:11:10.639 --> 00:11:12.279
Do we truly have a choice?

00:11:21.720 --> 00:11:22.200
No.

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:23.840
I promised her

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:24.720
I'd see her.

00:11:25.279 --> 00:11:26.879
Or she'll be worried and scared.

00:11:28.799 --> 00:11:29.559
After seeing her,

00:11:30.120 --> 00:11:32.080
I'll accept any punishment demanded.

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:33.480
Immortals, form the array!

00:11:40.059 --> 00:11:43.019
Sword Master, reflect on your actions.

00:12:39.899 --> 00:12:42.220
The Immortal Lord instructed me
to deliver this.

00:12:48.899 --> 00:12:49.820
Where's Wan Guchen?

00:12:50.539 --> 00:12:52.620
He was executed
for defying the Immortal Lord.

00:12:53.059 --> 00:12:54.620
He held this jade pendant when he died.

00:13:02.360 --> 00:13:03.159
It can't be.

00:13:06.080 --> 00:13:06.759
It can't be!

00:13:08.480 --> 00:13:09.840
You're lying, aren't you?

00:13:20.139 --> 00:13:21.340
He's such a good man.

00:13:23.779 --> 00:13:25.299
Why would you treat him like this?

00:13:26.019 --> 00:13:27.220
Tell me this is a lie!

00:13:27.620 --> 00:13:29.100
You must be lying!

00:13:29.100 --> 00:13:30.539
It's all your fault.

00:13:31.019 --> 00:13:32.899
Anyway, anyone involved with you

00:13:32.980 --> 00:13:34.139
couldn't possibly be good.

00:13:34.779 --> 00:13:36.620
He was never worthy
of being Sword Master.

00:13:36.700 --> 00:13:38.100
He deserved that lightning strike.

00:13:39.019 --> 00:13:39.539
No!

00:13:39.860 --> 00:13:40.779
You're lying!

00:13:41.539 --> 00:13:42.539
It can't be!

00:13:43.860 --> 00:13:44.779
It can't be.

00:13:45.100 --> 00:13:47.620
(What a despicable lackey.)

00:13:52.580 --> 00:13:53.299
Who's there?

00:13:56.019 --> 00:13:57.500
(Years of endurance)

00:13:58.139 --> 00:14:00.940
(only brought news
of your beloved's death.)

00:14:02.580 --> 00:14:04.659
(Will you keep enduring this?)

00:14:20.700 --> 00:14:22.500
Since you killed Chen,

00:14:23.899 --> 00:14:25.659
prepare to join him in death!

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:52.360
Night Deity,

00:14:53.080 --> 00:14:54.559
it's been too long.

00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:57.039
Indeed it has,

00:14:57.639 --> 00:14:59.159
Immortal Changgeng.

00:15:00.840 --> 00:15:03.320
Every torment this vessel endured

00:15:03.720 --> 00:15:05.159
remains etched in my memory.

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:09.519
Had the Nine Heavens not pushed so hard,

00:15:10.679 --> 00:15:12.799
I might not have awakened so soon.

00:15:14.679 --> 00:15:16.919
Now that you've killed Wan Guchen,

00:15:18.360 --> 00:15:20.440
I'll return the favor by killing you

00:15:21.799 --> 00:15:25.080
as fulfilling this girl's wish.

00:15:26.139 --> 00:15:26.820
Bai Yixi!

00:15:27.860 --> 00:15:29.179
Wan Guchen isn't dead.

00:15:30.679 --> 00:15:31.519
What?

00:15:31.940 --> 00:15:32.519
Yixi!

00:15:47.580 --> 00:15:49.248
The Immortal Lord
injured me unwillingly.

00:15:49.400 --> 00:15:50.850
He let an Upper Immortal treat me.

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:53.220
My injuries prevented me
from meeting you.

00:15:54.980 --> 00:15:56.580
So I asked them to deliver the pendant.

00:15:58.580 --> 00:15:59.379
Wan Guchen.

00:16:05.019 --> 00:16:06.659
Changgeng, you lied to me!

00:16:07.019 --> 00:16:07.700
Wan Guchen,

00:16:08.139 --> 00:16:09.019
you see it now.

00:16:09.620 --> 00:16:11.860
You can see what Bai Yixi
is destined to become.

00:16:12.379 --> 00:16:14.940
Imagine the devastation she'll cause!

00:16:17.980 --> 00:16:18.620
Kill her.

00:16:19.620 --> 00:16:20.500
Kill her now!

00:16:20.919 --> 00:16:22.000
Only by killing her

00:16:22.250 --> 00:16:24.648
can the Night Deity be stopped
from harming the Three Realms.

00:16:26.100 --> 00:16:27.100
Wan Guchen!

00:16:32.240 --> 00:16:32.960
Wan Guchen,

00:16:33.799 --> 00:16:35.519
don't you remember our promise?

00:16:42.259 --> 00:16:43.220
Why are you waiting?

00:16:43.539 --> 00:16:44.720
Once he breaks the seal

00:16:44.899 --> 00:16:46.879
and completely takes over
Bai Yixi's body,

00:16:47.220 --> 00:16:49.220
there'll be no way
to bring Bai Yixi back.

00:16:52.139 --> 00:16:53.059
Do it!

00:16:53.940 --> 00:16:54.980
Do it now!

00:17:22.420 --> 00:17:23.180
Chen,

00:17:26.339 --> 00:17:28.420
I don't want the Night Deity
to steal my body.

00:17:29.660 --> 00:17:30.460
I beg you.

00:17:31.460 --> 00:17:32.500
Please help me!

00:17:34.140 --> 00:17:35.140
Please...

00:17:59.460 --> 00:18:00.119
No.

00:18:08.380 --> 00:18:09.220
Wan Guchen,

00:18:09.619 --> 00:18:11.259
do you have any idea what you're doing?

00:18:11.779 --> 00:18:13.380
Your lingering ties with the Night Deity

00:18:13.660 --> 00:18:15.539
will bring endless calamity.

00:18:27.779 --> 00:18:28.900
I'll take Yixi away.

00:18:30.380 --> 00:18:31.900
So she can never harm anyone.

00:18:33.220 --> 00:18:33.500
You...

00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:47.800
The Divine Sword is sealed.

00:18:48.779 --> 00:18:49.660
Starting today,

00:18:50.940 --> 00:18:52.740
I'll leave the Nine Heavens with you.

00:18:57.819 --> 00:18:59.059
Where else can we go?

00:19:01.720 --> 00:19:03.839
I'm terrified
the Night Deity might reappear.

00:19:07.180 --> 00:19:07.980
Don't overthink it.

00:19:10.059 --> 00:19:10.900
I'll accompany you

00:19:11.480 --> 00:19:12.519
wherever you want to go.

00:19:15.259 --> 00:19:16.339
I'll always stay with you.

00:19:18.900 --> 00:19:19.380
Then

00:19:21.099 --> 00:19:23.440
I want to visit
where you lived as a child.

00:19:26.140 --> 00:19:26.579
Okay.

00:19:27.240 --> 00:19:27.839
I'll show you.

00:19:28.700 --> 00:19:29.140
Okay.

00:19:35.660 --> 00:19:37.259
Is this your hometown?

00:19:38.770 --> 00:19:40.370
It's my first visit to the Mortal Realm.

00:19:40.819 --> 00:19:41.579
Do you like it?

00:19:46.299 --> 00:19:46.819
Miss,

00:19:48.339 --> 00:19:49.259
buy a flower wreath?

00:19:55.680 --> 00:19:56.680
What is this flower?

00:19:57.500 --> 00:19:58.299
It's beautiful.

00:19:59.259 --> 00:20:00.380
I've never seen it before.

00:20:02.960 --> 00:20:04.079
It's the Knotgrass Flower.

00:20:04.700 --> 00:20:05.740
A wreath of knots

00:20:07.299 --> 00:20:08.059
all for one.

00:20:12.619 --> 00:20:14.019
With this wreath,

00:20:14.019 --> 00:20:15.380
you look like an immortal lady.

00:20:15.380 --> 00:20:16.339
Truly breathtaking.

00:20:16.680 --> 00:20:17.400
It's yours.

00:20:17.599 --> 00:20:18.160
No charge.

00:20:21.059 --> 00:20:23.019
If there's someone in this world
who's all for me,

00:20:23.880 --> 00:20:24.680
then my life journey

00:20:25.599 --> 00:20:26.640
is never in vain.

00:20:33.119 --> 00:20:33.799
Look.

00:20:37.850 --> 00:20:39.650
They say if you write wishes
on a sky lantern,

00:20:40.160 --> 00:20:41.079
they'll come true.

00:20:43.640 --> 00:20:44.599
They're beautiful.

00:20:45.799 --> 00:20:46.240
Let's go.

00:20:46.680 --> 00:20:47.400
I'll show you.

