Yixi.

00:25:44.299 --> 00:25:44.779
Yixi!

00:25:45.160 --> 00:25:45.839
It's me, Chen.

00:25:46.359 --> 00:25:46.799
Yixi,

00:25:47.759 --> 00:25:49.039
resist the Night Deity.

00:25:49.400 --> 00:25:49.839
Yixi!

00:25:58.500 --> 00:25:59.259
If this

00:26:00.200 --> 00:26:01.599
can ease your suffering,

00:26:02.460 --> 00:26:03.339
I'll endure

00:26:04.140 --> 00:26:05.019
however much you take.

00:26:13.019 --> 00:26:13.619
Yixi,

00:26:15.359 --> 00:26:16.700
no matter how you change,

00:26:18.140 --> 00:26:19.619
I'll always recognize you.

00:26:21.019 --> 00:26:21.980
Because I know

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:25.480
you'd never harm me.

00:26:32.119 --> 00:26:32.759
Yixi!

00:26:52.500 --> 00:26:53.099
What's wrong?

00:26:53.740 --> 00:26:54.299
Nightmare?

00:26:57.420 --> 00:26:57.980
I'm fine.

00:26:59.059 --> 00:27:00.180
But I feel

00:27:00.819 --> 00:27:02.980
the Night Deity's power within me
is harder to control.

00:27:03.579 --> 00:27:05.500
I don't know when it'll break free

00:27:06.140 --> 00:27:06.980
and hurt you again.

00:27:08.579 --> 00:27:09.220
Chen,

00:27:10.819 --> 00:27:11.940
I'm so scared.

00:27:12.940 --> 00:27:15.059
I'm scared I'll be fully consumed by it

00:27:15.900 --> 00:27:17.019
and lose my mind.

00:27:18.059 --> 00:27:20.619
Then I might forget everything
between us.

00:27:20.619 --> 00:27:21.019
Never.

00:27:22.900 --> 00:27:23.539
With me here,

00:27:24.940 --> 00:27:26.500
you won't face all this alone.

00:27:28.900 --> 00:27:30.900
I'll prepare some calming herbs.

00:27:31.940 --> 00:27:32.460
Fear not.

00:27:33.700 --> 00:27:34.740
We'll get through this.

00:27:53.888 --> 00:27:55.119
Yes. It's him!

00:27:56.380 --> 00:27:56.780
Back then,

00:27:57.019 --> 00:27:58.259
I saw that woman

00:27:58.579 --> 00:27:59.168
was like...

00:28:01.539 --> 00:28:02.900
"It hurts so much."

00:28:03.319 --> 00:28:05.279
"Let me bite you."

00:28:09.000 --> 00:28:09.720
The Night Deity

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:11.799
drained his life force back then.

00:28:12.079 --> 00:28:13.200
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:28:13.279 --> 00:28:14.440
No doubt about it!

00:28:14.599 --> 00:28:15.440
Wan Guchen,

00:28:16.319 --> 00:28:19.319
how dare you bring Bai Yixi,
that demon, to Wanfeng Kingdom!

00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:22.799
You're risking all the kingdom's lives.

00:28:23.640 --> 00:28:24.920
You truly are a curse!

00:28:24.920 --> 00:28:26.359
Exactly! A monster!

00:28:26.480 --> 00:28:27.000
A curse!

00:28:27.599 --> 00:28:28.079
Right!

00:28:28.559 --> 00:28:29.559
You knew you were cursed,

00:28:29.839 --> 00:28:30.599
yet came back!

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:31.559
And you even

00:28:31.600 --> 00:28:32.599
brought a devil with you.

00:28:32.880 --> 00:28:34.480
It was deliberate!

00:28:34.480 --> 00:28:36.440
How could the royal family
produce such filth!

00:28:36.640 --> 00:28:37.759
Pure evil!

00:28:38.359 --> 00:28:40.640
The Night Deity kills mercilessly.

00:28:40.799 --> 00:28:42.400
One glance at her

00:28:43.000 --> 00:28:44.359
and you're dead by dawn.

00:28:44.799 --> 00:28:45.920
What should we do?

00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:50.940
She's possessed by the Night Deity.

00:28:51.700 --> 00:28:52.700
She's innocent.

00:28:54.599 --> 00:28:56.819
