Xiaochuan!

00:29:22.900 --> 00:29:23.779
Don't hurt him!

00:29:28.440 --> 00:29:29.039
Xiaochuan!

00:29:30.880 --> 00:29:33.440
Mother, I don't think he's evil.

00:29:33.440 --> 00:29:36.240
Having a demon sealed inside is sad.

00:29:36.440 --> 00:29:38.519
You won't kill anyone, right?

00:29:40.359 --> 00:29:41.160
I promise

00:29:42.079 --> 00:29:43.200
