00:29:48.660 --> 00:29:49.099
Xiaochuan!

00:29:50.039 --> 00:29:50.720
Where is he?

00:29:52.240 --> 00:29:53.680
Useless fools!

00:30:05.839 --> 00:30:06.480
Yixi!

00:30:07.220 --> 00:30:07.660
Yixi!

00:30:11.339 --> 00:30:11.819
Yixi!

00:30:13.180 --> 00:30:13.940
