00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:16.360
Is the demonic energy flaring up?

00:30:17.380 --> 00:30:17.900
Yixi.

00:30:18.976 --> 00:30:20.299
Don't shut me out. Let me in.

00:30:20.299 --> 00:30:20.980
I can help you!

00:30:22.259 --> 00:30:22.819
Yixi!

